title: Star Trek: Picard
story: Patrick Stewart is that the executive producer of the series and stars as Picard, reprising his role from Star Trek: subsequent Generation also as other Star Trek media. Santiago Cabrera, Michelle Hurd, Evan Evagora, Alison Pill, Harry Treadaway, and Isa Briones also star. Several actors from the previous Star Trek series also reprise their roles, including Brent Spiner, Jeri Ryan, Marina Sirtis, and Jonathan Frakes. The series was first rumored in June 2018 when Kurtzman began his expansion and was officially announced that August after months of negotiations with Stewart, who had previously said he wouldn’t return to the franchise after Nemesis. Filming began in California in April 2019, with the series’ official title announced a month later.
